                      </th>
                      <th class="px-5 py-3 text-left text-[10px] font-black text-green-500/70 uppercase tracking-widest w-1/4">
                        Actividad Temporal
                      </th>
                      <th class="px-5 py-3 text-center text-[10px] font-black text-green-500/70 uppercase tracking-widest w-1/3">
                        Estado de Recursos
                      </th>
                      <th class="px-5 py-3 text-right text-[10px] font-black text-green-500/70 uppercase tracking-widest">
